			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>if you want the ultimate one shot glass cannon, well more than that but hey it's great fun/easy ;)<br />
make an Occultist<br />
take the DREEG'S EVIL EYE skill, you don't need ot increase it's power at start unless you wish to , instead push mastery points up so you can unlock FOCUSED EYE for Dreeg's Evil Eye<br />
turns the spammable acid/poison nuke/DoT, into a gigantic UBER nuke/DoT!<br />
can't spam it any more, 4 sec recast but ye gods it melts ANYTHING it hits :hulk:<br />
use it to waste bosses and groups of enemies<br />
<br />
work on collecting things that boost Acid/poison damage and power regen<br />
<br />
the Raven pet with 1st heal ability will help you and any other pets/players stay alive<br />
<br />
blood of dreg gives great group acid damage, health regen, acid retaliation<br />
<br />
hell hound pet helps keep you alive<br />
<br />
Sigil of Consumption gives a prolonged ground based zone that gives Life Stealing to anything you harm in it, can be upgraded to do damage itself as well<br />
<br />
Curse of Frailty slows movement and debuffs them, upgraded form also further degrades various resists so hitting an enemy with that THEN Dreeg's Evil Eye can 2 or 3 hit kill many bosses :p<br />
<br />
I'd suggest taking 2nd class in Arcanist<br />
Inner Focus increase power and magic damage for both classes<br />
Panetti's Replicating Missile as my basic nuke (I don't' use weapons except for their boosts to magical effects etc)<br />
Mirror of Eroctes as an &quot;invulnerability&quot; for when things go FUBAR<br />
<br />
my 2 cents :)</div>

